rget unit</dt><dd govuksummarylistrowvalue="" class="govuk-summary-list__value"><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><span>250,000</span><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></dd><!--container--><!--container--></div><div govuksummarylistrow="" class="govuk-summary-list__row"><dt govuksummarylistrowkey="" class="govuk-summary-list__key">Have you used the special reporting mechanism to adjust the baseline throughput for any of the facilities in the target unit using combined heat and power (CHP)?</dt><dd govuksummarylistrowvalue="" class="govuk-summary-list__value"><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><span>Yes</span><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></dd><!--container--><!--container--></div><div govuksummarylistrow="" class="govuk-summary-list__row"><dt govuksummarylistrowkey="" class="govuk-summary-list__key">Baseline throughput (MWh)</dt><dd govuksummarylistrowvalue="" class="govuk-summary-list__value"><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><span>75,000</span><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></dd><!--container--><!--container--></div><div govuksummarylistrow="" class="govuk-summary-list__row"><dt govuksummarylistrowkey="" class="govuk-summary-list__key">Performance (kWh/MWh)</dt><dd govuksummarylistrowvalue="" class="govuk-summary-list__value"><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><span>3.33</span><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></dd><!--container--><!--container--></div><div govuksummarylistrow="" class="govuk-summary-list__row"><dt govuksummarylistrowkey="" class="govuk-summary-list__key">Baseline energy to carbon factor (kgC/kWh)</dt><dd govuksummarylistrowvalue="" class="govuk-summary-list__value"><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><span>0.233</span><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></dd><!--container--><!--container--></div><!--container--><!--container--><!